<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>159</hymn_number>
<key>Bb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Jesuh cu ka Tuukhal a si, Zeihmanh ka tih ti lo, Ram hring lakah a ka
 ihter, Ti pawngah a ka hruai.

[V2]
 Ka nunnak kha a tlunter than, A min thangthat awk ca'h, A kut in
 dinnak lam tha ah, A ka kalpi lengmang.

[V3]
 Thihnak hor ah kal hmanhning law, Ka thin a phang lai lo, Na
 thiangthunh le na tanbo nih, Ka hna an ka ngamter.

[V4]
 Keimah ka ral hna hmaika ah, Rawl kha na ka dangh i, Ka lu kha chiti
 na thuh i, Ka hrai kha a liam ko.

[V5]
 Thatnak le zaangfahnak hna nih, An ka zulh camcin lai, Bawipa Pathian
 innchung ahcun, Zungzal in ka um lai.</lyrics>
<title>BAWIPA CU KA TUUKHAL A SI CH159</title>
</song>